Not a lot else to report

00:01:04.900 --> 00:01:08.867
As I said everything’s on track and feeling 
 good, and everything is still quite easy

00:01:09.633 --> 00:01:13.833
The other thing I wanted to talk about was 
 the number of drinks I’m having per day

00:01:14.567 --> 00:01:19.533
What I have done in the past I have been 
 trying to have about 500mls three times a day

00:01:14.567 --> 00:01:19.533
What I have done in the past I have been 
 trying to have about 500mls three times a day

00:01:19.933 --> 00:01:24.500
Which is somewhere between 16 to 18 fluid 
 ounces I think, for you US folk

00:01:25.467 --> 00:01:31.300
And what I have found in the past few days is that 
 I haven’t been feeling hungry at all during lunch time

00:01:31.800 --> 00:01:38.133
So I have had something at breakfast, and then something in the evening. And I 
 have just found that I don’t want to have any juice at lunch time

00:01:38.633 --> 00:01:44.430
So I have done that for two days in a row. I am not consciously trying to 
 avoid it. I just feel I don’t need it, so I’m not thinking about it

00:01:45.300 --> 00:01:49.230
Anyone else out there having a similar thing? I would be 
 interested to know whether that’s happening for you as well

00:01:50.100 --> 00:01:54.600
I am making sure though that I drink plenty of 
 fluid, because it’s obviously important to keep hydrated

00:01:55.100 --> 00:02:00.170
So if you are cutting back your juices a little bit, make 
 sure you’re topping up with water and having plenty of water

00:02:01.700 --> 00:02:03.700
And I do tend to avoid drinking low calorie 
 smoothies, since I’m focusing more on juices

00:02:02.600 --> 00:02:07.600
Of course, the other thing is, if you try 
 and actively stop giving yourself too much juice

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:10.770
Thinking that perhaps you’re going to lose some more weight

00:02:11.533 --> 00:02:14.100
Your body can go into a protection, survival type mode

00:02:30.433 --> 00:02:35.030
But anyway, what I was saying was if you are trying to cut back, and 
 thinking, well, I’m only going to have one or two juices a day

00:02:35.533 --> 00:02:41.470
