 actually thinks that there is a problem with you getting enough nutrition

00:02:42.200 --> 00:02:43.830
And that hinders your weight loss

00:02:46.733 --> 00:02:48.070
Make sure you don’t do that purposely. Also do avoid energy 
 drinks since they have a lot of energy drink dangers

